Package: nginx-gone
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends},
         ${misc:Depends},
         nginx (>= 1.18.0)
Description: Nginx module to return HTTP 410 Gone for listed URIs
 This module reads a URI list from a map file at configuration
 time and returns HTTP 410 Gone for matching requests. Supports
 exact string matches and PCRE regex patterns. Useful for cleanly
 handling permanently removed URLs without map+if workarounds.
